WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy C2-M03: School, study and work. Learners practise control irony and implication through classroom language, learning habits, jobs, workplace communication. The teacher models idiomaticity and collocation, introduces vocabulary such as subjects, study skills, jobs, duties, workplace phrases, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
